beachcomber
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:A prospector or miner who works black-sand beaches for gold, a new goldfields formation from beach n2.  (cf beach claim), and comb @v and comber @n,  (cf beacher); and perhaps associated with the  older beachcomber 1. above.


